channel.title: Comments on: Blog changes
channel.description: I am multiple and various - Tomas A. Krag

item.title: By: Daen de Leon
item.dc:creator: Daen de Leon
item.description:
Ha! You thought you were blogging away in anonymity. I've got news for you, sunshine ... secretly, this blog is being syndicated to 57 news agencies from Afghanistan to Zimbabwe ;-)
Isn't GeoUrl a wonderful thing?
